{"tid":2121947,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"英國政府聲明：BNO護照是合法國際旅行證件","createTime":"2020-07-23T15:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T15:57:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"74f254848d37e760f9d580451a7f1618bc00fa2f","tid":2121947,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539545-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539545-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCFBOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=c3a90c02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539545-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6aac6c49\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539545-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜的發言人表示，英國國民海外護照BNO是一種合法的國際旅行證件，護照持有人可以期待得到相應的對待。<br />\n<br />\n英國在星期三宣布，允許有資格申請BNO的港人和近親，明年一月起，申請居留及入籍安排。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部堅決反對英方在BNO問題上執意搞政治操弄，將考慮不承認BNO作為有效旅行證件，並保留採取進一步措施的權利。"}]}